an cut windows between worlds. As Lyra learns the truth about her parents and her prophesied destiny, the two young people are caught up in a war against celestial powers that ranges across many worlds and leads to a thrilling conclusion in The Amber Spyglass.','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2RjNWQzNTQtMmY4Yi00Yzk5LWFiODItY2EyZjBmNjZmYmI2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTkxNjUyNQ@@._V1_SX101_CR0,0,101,150_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2RjNWQzNTQtMmY4Yi00Yzk5LWFiODItY2EyZjBmNjZmYmI2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTkxNjUyNQ@@.jpg'),(212,'Watchmen',2019,1,_binary '\0',7049682,360733,'Set in an alternate history where masked vigilantes are treated as outlaws and must embrace the nostalgia, Detective Angela Abar investigates the reemergence of a white supremacist terrorist group inspired by the long-deceased moral absolutist Rorschach.','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYjhhZDE3NjgtMjkzNC00NzI3LWJhOTItMWQ5ZjljODA5NWNkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzQ2MDI5NjU@._V1_SX101_CR0,0,101,150_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYjhhZDE3NjgtMjkzNC00NzI3LWJhOTItMWQ5ZjljODA5NWNkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzQ2MDI5NjU@.jpg'),(213,'Batwoman',2019,2,_binary '',8712204,361315,'Kate Kane, armed with a passion for social justice and a flair for speaking her mind, soars onto the streets of Gotham as Batwoman, an out lesbian and highly trained street fighter primed to snuff out the failing city\'s criminal resurgence. But don\'t call her a hero yet. In a city desperate for a savior, Kate must overcome her own demons before embracing the call to be Gotham\'s symbol of hope.','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTFlYjVlZmEtODhhMS00MjA4LWI1MjEtNGJkMWQ1YWZiY2QzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDQ0MTYzMDA@._V1_SY150_CR5,0,101,150_.jpg','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTFlYjVlZmEtODhhMS00MjA4LWI1MjEtNGJkMWQ1YWZiY2QzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDQ0MTYzMDA@.jpg'),(214,'Raising Dion',2019,2,_binary '',7826108,335985,'No plot ouline','https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZTgyYjZjMzktNjk1OC00ZDdmLThmODEtNzUxMzcyY2Y1YzBmXk